tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE LandTypes (land_type_id INT PRIMARY KEY, land_type_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL, land_type_description TEXT) 

CREATE TABLE Classifications (classification_id INT PRIMARY KEY, classification_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL, classification_value FLOAT)

CREATE TABLE mapping_data (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    map_id INT NOT NULL,
    land_type_id INT NOT NULL,
    classification_id INT NOT NULL,
    map_data JSONB
);
